data.description: Welcome to 73800 Flagstone Lane nestled at the end of the quiet cul-de-sac just blocks from fine dining and shopping on El Paseo. Come see this beautifully remodeled golf course and mountain view home. This sprawling and open floorplan home has multiple living and dining spaces all filled with natural light and flow seamlessly from one to another. The 3 spacious bedrooms all have their own ensuite bathroom and walk-in closet. The open kitchen with extensive counter space, views of the front and backyards and a large walk-in pantry is a must see. New cabinets, quartz countertops and all brand-new appliances make for the ideal place to entertain and is perfect for any home chef. The private and secluded backyard is all tied together by an oversized bonus space, making it the perfect spot for a guest room or additional family entertainment space. The upgraded pool and spa equipment make for easy maintenance and peace of mind. The home also features new flooring and recessed lighting throughout the home. Leaving the best for last, the sunset views and peaceful evenings on the back patio are what desert living is all about.
